                     <interp inst="t18760228-232-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, Stealing a brown paper parcel containing three dozen towels and three blinds, of the value together of 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18760228-name-173" type="victimName">
